sequenceDiagram
    participant A as Developer A
    participant GH as GitHub
    participant B as Developer B
    A->>A: git checkout -b feature/x
    A->>A: code + commit
    A->>GH: git push origin feature/x
    A->>GH: Create Pull Request
    B->>GH: Review code
    GH->>GH: Merge to main
    B->>B: git pull
